-- Monte Paschi shares suspended after 9 pct drop 
-- 
-- Fri Oct 31, 2014 05:59AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, Oct 31 (Reuters) - Shares in Monte dei Paschi <BMPS.MI> fell 9.5 percent before trading was suspended on Friday, bringing their overall fall since a 2 billion euro capital shortfall at the Italian bank was unveiled on Sunday close to 40 percent.

